{"tid":1602381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和警察對峙避無可避，合理非以無罪之身應主動被拉","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T11:43:52.000Z","uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3276ea584914ef9a9db1e8b89c992b33b0d0f39","tid":1602381,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"好多人話抗爭失焦，唔應該花大量精力同警察對峙，但如果對家刻意如此安排，和警察對峙是不可避免。<br />\n因此，問題應該係如何營造受害者身份，警察激化矛盾，一路試圖制造警察之死意圖扭轉輿論，對應策略可以是，勇武打遊擊制造破壞，要有華麗的視覺效果，合理非墊後，準備被拉。沒錯，合理非要有被拉的準備，甚至可能被毆打，但這就制造了文宣效果且合理非其實並無違法，被拉之後也能最終安然而退。<br />\n大家回憶一下過去一段時間最撼動人心的是何種視頻，比如陳伯被噴胡椒粉。合理非因考慮用無罪之身被拉，放大港共魔警的罪惡。<br />\n已經無人可以獨善其身了。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d494987d73d7140547f254f83e400a13a622ffb1","tid":1602381,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2331bf1866354b033373015498de752e1abd8bf","tid":1602381,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"準備同主動唔同喎..."},{"pid":"355100b0991644447c513004b9ad80dffb493c6c","tid":1602381,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"51831b29fccb23480bd9d954f39d181f7ed95405","tid":1602381,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何式凝左膠 </span>"},{"pid":"9d6d7700b4b93275e68be54c6f68398e7ceecd30","tid":1602381,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"e03b804776e9e5c3f8e465bd2ebb49b597f5d11f","tid":1602381,"uid":266959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s